* PP_OFF sets to Start/End of the OFF period range
*   %1 - OFF Set name
*   %2 - 'C'ommodity/'P'rocess index indicator
*   %3 - control set
*   %4 - Table to set for each off-range with qualifier and one open (
*   %5 - The value for the off range (EPS/NO)
